text: The Laborec () is a river in eastern Slovakia. It flows through the towns of Medzilaborce, Humenné, Strážske and Michalovce. The river is long. The main tributaries of this river include the Uzh, which flows into the Laborec near the village of Drahňov and the Cirocha river.
